metadata.value: Launched on September 15th 2020 and in continuous operations Vigor Protocol is a multi-asset, self balancing, fully collateralized crypto lending and borrowing protocol. It is unique in all crypto as it adjusts for solvency autonomously based on its DAC member’s User interactions and the high speed data feed from the equally reliable Delphi Oracle soon to be releasing its new QED version. Vigor Protocols unique approach is impractical on any EVM blockchain and only feasible running on faster lower cost Antelope based Blockchains. There is no human intervention setting rates or forced liquidations by auction it’s smart contracts do all the work. The Protocol enables you to borrow VIGOR, a “low volatility” token, which is backed by your crypto assets and earn rewards. Vigor Protocol’s smart contracts are designed to mimic the European Union’s Solvency II Protocol. Vigor allows you to reduce your exposure to crypto price volatility. Welcome to the future of Defi, reDeFined.
